<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Parachute — NVC Pitch Deck</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;1,9..40,400&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400&display=swap">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg:           #faf8f4;
            --bg-soft:      #f3f0ea;
            --fg:           #2c2a26;
            --fg-muted:     #6b6860;
            --fg-dim:       #9a9690;
            --accent:       #4a7c59;
            --accent-soft:  rgba(74, 124, 89, 0.08);
            --accent-light: #6a9b77;
            --border:       #e4e0d8;
            --serif: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
            --sans:  'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
            --mono:  'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        }

        *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; scroll-snap-type: y mandatory; }

        body {
            background: var(--bg);
            font-family: var(--sans);
            color: var(--fg);
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .slide {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 4rem 6rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            scroll-snap-align: start;
            position: relative;
        }
        .slide:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

        .slide-label {
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.14em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .slide-headline {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5.5vw, 4.5rem);
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            line-height: 1.08;
            color: var(--fg);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .slide-headline em { font-style: italic; color: var(--fg-muted); }

        .slide-sub {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--fg-muted);
            max-width: 600px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .slide-sub strong { color: var(--fg); font-weight: 500; }

        /* -- Speaker notes -- */
        .speaker-notes {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--bg-soft);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 700px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--fg-muted);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .speaker-notes .notes-label {
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        body.show-notes .speaker-notes { display: block; }

        /* -- Notes toggle -- */
        .notes-toggle {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 1.5rem;
            right: 1.5rem;
            z-index: 100;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            background: var(--fg);
            color: var(--bg);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-family: var(--sans);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            opacity: 0.7;
            transition: opacity 0.15s;
        }
        .notes-toggle:hover { opacity: 1; }

        /* -- Stat row -- */
        .stat-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #fff;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        .stat {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }
        .stat-num {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            line-height: 1;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--fg-muted);
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        /* -- Flywheel -- */
        .flywheel {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        .fw-step {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            color: var(--fg);
            padding: 0.85rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }
        .fw-step:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .fw-step.final { color: var(--accent); }
        .fw-num {
            font-family: var(--mono);
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            color: var(--fg-dim);
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* -- Tier table -- */
        .tier-table {
            margin: 1rem 0;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #fff;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        .tier-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: baseline;
            gap: 1.25rem;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.25rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .tier-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .tier-price {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            min-width: 4.5rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .tier-price span { font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--fg-dim); }
        .tier-body { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--fg-muted); }
        .tier-body strong { color: var(--fg); font-weight: 500; }
        .tier-highlight { background: var(--accent-soft); }

        /* -- Ask box -- */
        .ask-box {
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #fff;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        .ask-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: baseline;
            padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .ask-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .ask-row .lbl { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--fg-muted); }
        .ask-row .val { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--fg); }

        .close-quote {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
            color: var(--fg);
            margin-top: 2.5rem;
            line-height: 1.3;
            max-width: 550px;
        }
        .close-links {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--fg-dim);
        }
        .close-links a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
        .close-links a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

        /* -- Architecture diagram -- */
        .arch-diagram {
            margin: 1rem 0;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #fff;
            max-width: 650px;
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0;
        }
        .arch-spoke { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
        .arch-spoke-label {
            font-family: var(--mono);
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--fg-dim);
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }
        .arch-spoke.right { align-items: flex-end; }
        .arch-spoke.right .arch-spoke-label { text-align: right; }
        .arch-box {
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--fg);
            background: var(--bg);
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .arch-hub {
            border: 2px solid var(--accent);
            background: var(--accent-soft);
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 500;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin: 0 0.25rem;
        }
        .arch-hub strong { display: block; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .arch-connector {
            font-family: var(--mono);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--fg-dim);
            padding: 0 0.5rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.15rem;
        }
        .arch-connector .conn-label {
            font-size: 0.55rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* -- Competitor landscape -- */
        .landscape {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 0;
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .landscape-quadrant {
            padding: 1.25rem;
            border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .landscape-quadrant:nth-child(2n) { border-right: none; }
        .landscape-quadrant:nth-child(n+3) { border-bottom: none; }
        .landscape-quadrant .quad-label {
            font-size: 0.55rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--fg-dim);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .landscape-quadrant .quad-names {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: var(--fg-muted);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .landscape-quadrant.ours { background: var(--accent-soft); }
        .landscape-quadrant.ours .quad-label { color: var(--accent); }
        .landscape-quadrant.ours .quad-names { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }

        /* -- Persona cards -- */
        .persona-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            max-width: 900px;
        }
        .persona-card {
            flex: 1;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .persona-card .persona-who {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: var(--fg);
            margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
        }
        .persona-card .persona-how {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--fg-muted);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* -- GTM channels -- */
        .gtm-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            max-width: 700px;
        }
        .gtm-item {
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .gtm-item .gtm-name {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--fg);
        }

        /* -- Mobile -- */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .slide { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
            .stat-row { flex-direction: column; }
            .stat { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
            .stat:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
            .landscape { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .landscape-quadrant { border-right: none !important; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border) !important; }
            .landscape-quadrant:last-child { border-bottom: none !important; }
            .persona-row { flex-direction: column; }
            .gtm-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Download bar -->
    <div style="position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; background: var(--bg); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 0.75rem 2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;">
        <span style="font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--fg);">Parachute &mdash; NVC Pitch Deck</span>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem;">
            <a href="/nvc/ES_Parachute.pdf" download style="padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500;">Executive Summary (PDF)</a>
            <a href="/nvc/Parachute.pptx" download style="padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500;">Pitch Deck (PPTX)</a>
            <a href="/nvc/" style="padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem; background: var(--bg-soft); color: var(--fg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500;">Full Summary</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <button class="notes-toggle" onclick="document.body.classList.toggle('show-notes'); this.textContent = document.body.classList.contains('show-notes') ? 'Hide Notes' : 'Speaker Notes';">Speaker Notes</button>

    <!-- SLIDE 1: Aspiration -->
    <section class="slide" style="padding-top: 6rem;">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4rem;">
            <div style="flex: 1;">
                <h2 class="slide-headline">Your thinking, captured.<br>Your AI, <em>transformed.</em></h2>
                <p class="slide-sub">This is Parachute.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="flex: 0 0 auto;">
                <img src="/nvc/images/pendant-worn.png" alt="Parachute pendant worn on a walk" style="width: 340px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="speaker-notes">
            <div class="notes-label">Speaker Notes</div>
            Imagine going for a walk, talking through your ideas, and by the time you're home your thoughts are organized, searchable, and available to any AI you use. That's the experience we're building. I'm wearing the device right now.
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SLIDE 2: The Product -->
    <section class="slide">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4rem;">
            <div style="flex: 1;">
                <div class="slide-label">The Product</div>
                <h2 class="slide-headline">Parachute Daily.<br>Just talk.</h2>
                <p class="slide-sub">Voice-first journal. Pendant or phone.<br>Simple for humans. Native for AI.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="flex: 0 0 auto;">
                <img src="/nvc/images/pendant-render.png" alt="Parachute pendant" style="width: 240px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="speaker-notes">
            <div class="notes-label">Speaker Notes</div>
            Parachute Daily is a voice-first journal. You speak into a wearable pendant or your phone &mdash; on a walk, in the car, wherever thinking happens. Your thoughts get transcribed and structured into a personal knowledge graph. No learning curve, just talk. The pendant is a wearable voice capture device &mdash; press a button, talk, and your thoughts are structured by the time you're home. Working prototype, on stage today.
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SLIDE 3: The Problem -->
    <section class="slide">
        <div class="slide-label">The Problem</div>
        <h2 class="slide-headline">There&rsquo;s no<br>knowledge layer.</h2>
        <p class="slide-sub">Every AI stores your context as <strong>one flat text file.</strong><br>No structure. No portability. No depth.</p>
        <div class="speaker-notes">
            <div class="notes-label">Speaker Notes</div>
            Every AI platform &mdash; ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini &mdash; stores your personal context the same way: one big text file. It remembers your name, not six months of your thinking. And capture is broken: to give your AI context, you have to talk to your AI. There's no way to think for yourself and have it become context. We need tools that help us think for ourselves first, then think with AI. That quality of independent thinking is what makes AI most useful.
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SLIDE 4: How It Works -->
    <section class="slide">
        <div class="slide-label">How It Works</div>
        <h2 class="slide-headline">Spin up a vault.<br>Give any AI a link.</h2>
        <div class="arch-diagram">
            <div class="arch-spoke">
                <div class="arch-spoke-label">you</div>
                <span class="arch-box">Parachute Daily</span>
                <span class="arch-box">Pendant</span>
                <span class="arch-box">Phone &middot; Web</span>
            </div>
            <div class="arch-connector">&harr;</div>
            <div class="arch-hub">
                <strong>Parachute Vault</strong>
                Notes &middot; Tags &middot; Links
            </div>
            <div class="arch-connector">
                &harr;
                <span class="conn-label">MCP</span>
            </div>
            <div class="arch-spoke right">
                <div class="arch-spoke-label">your AI</div>
                <span class="arch-box">Claude</span>
                <span class="arch-box">ChatGPT</span>
                <span class="arch-box">Gemini</span>
                <span class="arch-box">Any agent</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="speaker-notes">
            <div class="notes-label">Speaker Notes</div>
            Your data lives in a personal knowledge graph &mdash; Notes, Tags, and Links &mdash; accessible to any AI via MCP, the open standard for connecting AI to tools. You spin up a vault in seconds and give any AI a link. That's it. Whatever AI you already use, Parachute makes it better. You don't switch anything &mdash; you add Parachute.
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SLIDE 5: Competitive Landscape -->
    <section class="slide">
        <div class="slide-label">Competitive Landscape</div>
        <h2 class="slide-headline">Everyone builds one piece.</h2>
        <div class="landscape">
            <div class="landscape-quadrant">
                <div class="quad-label">Note apps</div>
                <div class="quad-names">Obsidian<br>Apple Notes<br>Notion</div>
            </div>
            <div class="landscape-quadrant">
                <div class="quad-label">AI platforms</div>
                <div class="quad-names">ChatGPT<br>Gemini<br>Claude</div>
            </div>
            <div class="landscape-quadrant">
                <div class="quad-label">Knowledge tools</div>
                <div class="quad-names">Tana<br>Roam<br>Mem</div>
            </div>
            <div class="landscape-quadrant ours">
                <div class="quad-label">Parachute</div>
                <div class="quad-names">Open &middot; Portable &middot; Agent-native</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="speaker-notes">
            <div class="notes-label">Speaker Notes</div>
            Note apps like Obsidian and Apple Notes have great capture but no AI integration. AI platforms like ChatGPT and Gemini are smart but their memory is siloed &mdash; trapped inside one ecosystem. Knowledge tools like Tana and Roam are powerful but only for power users. Nobody connects them. Parachute is the knowledge layer that works across all of them. Open, portable, agent-native. We don't compete with anyone's AI &mdash; we make every AI better. And yes, Gemini and ChatGPT will eventually build something like this, but it'll be locked inside their walled garden. We're the layer that works across ecosystems.
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SLIDE 6: Who Uses This -->
    <section class="slide">
        <div class="slide-label">Real-World Usage</div>
        <h2 class="slide-headline">For anyone who thinks.</h2>
        <div class="persona-row">
            <div class="persona-card">
                <div class="persona-who">The Thinker</div>
                <div class="persona-how">Morning walk. Talk through ideas. AI already knows yesterday.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="persona-card">
                <div class="persona-who">The Professional</div>
                <div class="persona-how">Voice-notes after meetings. Months of context, any tool.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="persona-card">
                <div class="persona-who">The Enterprise</div>
                <div class="persona-how">Knowledge transfer. Expertise lives on in a queryable vault.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="speaker-notes">
            <div class="notes-label">Speaker Notes</div>
            Three real journeys. The thinker goes for a morning walk, talks through ideas, and their AI assistant already knows what they were mulling over yesterday. The professional voice-notes after every meeting &mdash; months of institutional context, searchable by any tool, never trapped in one app. And the enterprise use case: a departing team member records three days of knowledge transfer. Their expertise lives on in a structured, queryable vault. Baby boomers with five years left working, companies that want a smooth transition &mdash; there's a real enterprise pathway here.
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SLIDE 7: Context Compounds -->
    <section class="slide">
        <div class="slide-label">The Moat</div>
        <h2 class="slide-headline">Context compounds.</h2>
        <div class="flywheel">
            <div class="fw-step"><span class="fw-num">01</span> Capture thoughts</div>
            <div class="fw-step"><span class="fw-num">02</span> Build personal context</div>
            <div class="fw-step"><span class="fw-num">03</span> Connect any AI</div>
            <div class="fw-step"><span class="fw-num">04</span> AI already knows you</div>
            <div class="fw-step final"><span class="fw-num">&rarr;</span> Switching cost through genuine value</div>
        </div>
        <p class="slide-sub" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">Open source &middot; Local-first &middot; Public Benefit Corporation</p>
        <div class="speaker-notes">
            <div class="notes-label">Speaker Notes</div>
            Every note builds a richer graph. The longer you use it, the more valuable it becomes &mdash; and the harder it is to leave. But we're not locking anyone in. Your data is portable, exportable, self-hostable. We're open source, local-first, and a Public Benefit Corporation. The switching cost comes from genuine value, not vendor lock-in.
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SLIDE 8: Business Model + Market -->
    <section class="slide">
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 4rem; align-items: flex-start;">
            <div style="flex: 1;">
                <div class="slide-label">Business Model</div>
                <h2 class="slide-headline">The $2&ndash;10 add-on.</h2>
                <div class="tier-table">
                    <div class="tier-row">
                        <div class="tier-price">Free</div>
                        <div class="tier-body"><strong>Offline journal</strong></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tier-row">
                        <div class="tier-price">$2<span>/mo</span></div>
                        <div class="tier-body"><strong>Cloud sync + MCP</strong></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tier-row">
                        <div class="tier-price">$5<span>/mo</span></div>
                        <div class="tier-body"><strong>Cloud transcription</strong></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tier-row tier-highlight">
                        <div class="tier-price">$10<span>/mo</span></div>
                        <div class="tier-body"><strong>AI reflections + synthesis</strong></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tier-row">
                        <div class="tier-price">$100</div>
                        <div class="tier-body"><strong>Pendant</strong></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
